{
  "stem": "142.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 20.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I know that when we're in the wagon was-- I know we're together with the Venezia family together, the only family that was at that time together.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we-- we thought of escaping, but my father was adamant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't want to-- to have a thing like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then-- it was very difficult, because there was a-- a small window.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were barbed-- barbed wires there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how we could do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very, very difficult.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It took from the-- I know we arrived there the 11--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--from-- from the 2nd to the 11-- 9 days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it stop.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, that-- that wasn't a-- always, they-- they left passages for other trains that are more important.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we took nine days to go from-- from Athens to-- to Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only food that-- that we were were the food from the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think we weren't even hungry about this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was thinking, and thinking, and thinking-- mind goes wild.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know if we had any conversations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first thing that I remember is-- are the SS always, schnell!",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Schnell!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Schnell!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Right!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We got into line.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were-- Mengele was there, making the selection, always with his two fingers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Most of the fingers went on the-- on the right and-- which is going direct to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On the left was-- he was selecting 10% of the young of the-- every transport. 10% that we say went to work.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The others were direct to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I knew that after a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't remember step by step.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I can tell you that, there, there's nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After they selected you, it's very fast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everything is going fast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You go there, and then they take you.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
